Description: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character.  Enhances the accuracy of a power by {Boost.Attrib.Accuracy.Scale}%, damage by {Boost.Attrib.Damage.Scale}% and reduces endurance cost by {Boost.Attrib.Endurance.Scale}%.  This enhancement can only be slotted by Blasters and may be slotted into any Blaster damage power and requires the user to be level 50.     ATTUNED -- This enhancement's effective level is always the same as the user's.  In addition, its effectiveness will increase when the user levels up.
DisplayName: Superior Attuned Superior Defiant Barrage D
